CM_ "Version:V1.0.0,Date:2026/2/10,Author:yuzheyu,Review:,Approval:向宇设变,Description:(DSM)1、VIU_DSM_0x39A新增信号VIU_DrvrSeatStopAdjustCmd，VIU_Set1_3C0新增信号VIU_PassSeatStopAdjustCmd，VIU_LRSM_0x3D1新增信号VIU_ReleSeatStopAdjustCmd，VIU_RRSM_0x3E5新怎信号VIU_ReRiSeatStopAdjustCmd，VIU_RTSM_2E4新增信号VIU_3rdLSeatStopAdjustCmd，VIU_3rdRSeatStopAdjustCmd，VIU_RRSM_0x396新增信号VIU_ReRiSeatYAxisMotPosnSet，RRSM_St_0x555新增信号RRSM_YAxisMotPosn，VIU_RRSM_0x396新增信号VIU_ReRiSeatYAxisMotPosnStepSet，VIU_RTSM_0x395新增信号VIU_3rdRSeatBackrestMotPosnSet，VIU_3rdRSeatBackrestMotPosnStepSet，VIU_3rdLSeatBackrestMotPosnStepSet，VIU_3rdLSeatBackrestMotPosnSet，VIU_3rdRSeatFoldFunSet，VIU_3rdLSeatFoldFunSet，新增报文RTSM_St_0x554，涉及DSM,PSM,RRSM,RRSM_5Seat,VIU0_IP_EV,VIU0_IP_EVR,VIU1_CABIN；
2、取消报文VIU_RRSM_0x3E5中的RRSM_AP_current_slide，RRSM_AP_hall_slide，RRSM_ApTrigReasonSlide，新增报文RRSM_0x652，报文中新增信号RRSM_AP_current_slide，RRSM_AP_hall_slide，RRSM_ApTrigReasonSlide，涉及RRSM,VIU1_CABIN；;
Version:V1.1.2,Date:2026/3/20,Author:yuzheyu,Review:,Approval:向宇设变,Description:(DSM)1、报文VIU_Set1_3C0中新增信号VIU_PassbackrestHeatgLvl,VIU_PasscushionHeatgLvl,涉及VIU1_CABIN,PSM；
2、报文PSM_St2_0x556中新增信号PSM_PassSeatbackrestHeatgSts，PSM_PassSeatcushionHeatgSts.涉及VIU1_CABIN,PSM；
3、报文VIU_RRSM_0x396中新增信号VIU_ReRiSeatCushTiltMotPosnStepSet，涉及RRSM_5Seat,RRSM,VIU1_CABIN2；
4、报文VIU_RRSM_0x3E5中新增信号VIU_ReRibackrestHeatgLvl，VIU_ReRicushionHeatgLvl,涉及RRSM_5Seat,RRSM,VIU1_CABIN2；
