6、报文RRSM_St_546中新增信号RRSM_ReRiSeatbackrestHeatgSts,RRSM_ReRiSeatcushionHeatgSts,涉及RRSM_5Seat,RRSM,VIU1_CABIN2；
7、报文LRSM_St_0x3D2中新增信号LRSM_ReLeSeatbackrestHeatgSts,LRSM_ReLeSeatcushionHeatgSts,涉及RRSM_5Seat,VIU1_CABIN2,LRSM,VIU0_IP_EV,VIU0_IP_EVR；
8、报文VIU_DSM_0x39A中新增信号VIU_DrvrSeatLegSupportMotPosnStepSet，VIU_DrvrSeatLegExtnMotPosnStepSet,涉及DSM,VIU0_IP_EV,VIU0_IP_EVR；
9、报文VIU_Ctrl_0x39E中新增信号VIU_DrvrSeatbackrestHeatgLvl,VIU_DrvrSeatcushionHeatgLvl,涉及DSM,VIU0_IP_EV,VIU0_IP_EVR；
